cc:Work.dc:title: morning glory
cc:Work.dc:description: Morning glory is a common name for over 1,000 species.Most morning glory flowers curl up and close during the warm parts of the day, and are fully open in the morning, thus their name. \n \nIn this design i was actually experimenting with dew on the flowers which was achieved using oval shapes with semi-transparent fill and dark colored border from the primary subject color.
